ActIndian Act
SubjectWoodstock Indian Reserve No. 23, New Brunswick ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by the PROVINCE OF NEW BRUNSWICK of the power to take an interest in lands within WOODSTOCK INDIAN RESERVE NO. 23, New Brunswick; and (b) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the grant of the required easement.
